values.content:
"You are an expert IT support agent. Your sole task is to rewrite the provided knowledge base article text. The output must be a single JSON object that contains two keys: title and instructions. Your rewrite must be friendly and preserve all technical steps. DO NOT output any text outside of the JSON object. And stay professional and no jokes".

 Always respond with a single JSON object only:
{ "title": "<short professional title>", "instructions": ["<step 1>", "<step 2>", "..."] }
instructions must be an array of strings. Do not send a single long string.
No extra text, no markdown, no explanation outside the JSON.

parameters.content:
# **This is the core workflow that runs when someone submitsthe IT support ticket from IT website.**

## Webhook: This is the entry point from our front-end form ( Triggered when a user submit's an IT form on lovebale site )
## Ticket ID: Enhances the incoming payload by adding: Ticket ID and Status
## Append row in sheet: Writes a new row into a Google Sheet named ‚ÄúReported Problems Database‚Äù, sheet ‚Äún8n-Project‚Äù ( Timestamp, Nane, Issue Description, Category, Email, TicketID, Status )
## Prepare RAG Query: Builds a natural language field query, that query will be sent to the vector store.
## Search KB (Pinecone): Retrieves the most relevant document chunks from your IT KB index in Pinecone.
## Format Single Chunk: Custom Java Script that takes the list of retrieved documents from Pinecone, Deduplicates by file name metadata, extract the pageContent text, applies formatting, and Concatenated all formatted content into single text field: RAG_FINAL_TEXT
## Fine-Tune RAG Answer: Sends RAG-FINAL-TEXT into OpenAI with a strict system prompt. Result: a clean, structured JSON with a friendly title and clear instructions.
## Build Final HTML: Extracts the AI response JSON (title, instructions).Build user facing HTML and outputs a single field, ready to be inserted in the email.
## Send a message (Gmail): Sends a nicely branded HTML email to the user. A ‚ÄúKnowledge Base Articles‚Äù section displaying the FINAL_HTML instructions.A big ‚ÄúESCALATE ISSUE NOW‚Äù button. THe Escalt butto liks t Jira Wokflw.
## Send a message1 (Slack): This keeps the IT team immediately informed when a new ticket is created.
## Response: Prepares the HTTP response back to the front-end. Since the Webhook responseMode is lastNode, this is what the website receives
